Class Compute

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opentosca.toscana.model.BaseToscaElement

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    VisitableNode

    public class Compute
extends RootNode
    Represents one or more real or virtual processors of software applications or services along with other essential local resources. Collectively, the resources the compute node represents can logically be viewed as a (real or virtual) “server”. (TOSCA Simple Profile in YAML Version 1.1, p. 169)
